text: James Thomas Reid McManus (October 1, 1874 – November 11, 1948) was a Canadian politician. He served in the Legislative Assembly of New Brunswick as member of the Liberal party representing Westmorland County from 1921 to 1925. ==References== Category:20th-century Canadian politicians Category:1874 births Category:1948 deaths Category:New Brunswick Liberal Association MLAs
